Package shoppingcart

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Prod
    Product interface that helps create new product types
    ProdList<E>
    Interface to create a LinkedList adaptation
    User
    Interface that helps create new user types
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BundleProduct
    Bundle Product that handles a group of products, implements prod interface
    Customer
    A User object type that implements User interface and is responsible for Customer account
    DiscountProduct
    Discount Product that takes a Product and gives back a DiscountProduct type, Implements prod interface
    PDList<E>
    Collection Type object that adapts a LinkedList, implements ProdList
    Product
    Default product type that, implements prod
    Seller
    A User object type that implements User interface and is responsible for Seller account
    SystemAPI
    System API, each class controls a pages UI
    WrapLayout
    FlowLayout subclass that fully supports wrapping of components.
